arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorLorath, 2)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorLorath)
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(actorLorath, animKeyNeutral)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorLorath, locLorathPostIntroConvo, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorLorath, locLorathPostIntroConvo)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	-- disable optional dialogues during the scene
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(actorLorath, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(actorTaissa, false)
	
	--Lorath speaks and moves to pedestal
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convEye01, actorLorath)
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorLorath, 2)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(actorLorath, locEyeLorath, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_WALK, true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorLorath, locEyeLorath)

	--send advance event	
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(actorLorath, "QST_Conv_Keji1_01_Advance")
	Hydra.QActorAnim(actorLorath, animKeyPointLeft) 
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorIGCBook)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorIGCScroll01)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorIGCScroll02)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	-- Play IGC
	CampaignForcedPartyGatherPlayIGC(convRTC, idActorPlayer)
	
	
	Hydra.ActorDisable(gizmoSwitchPedestal)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorServerPropReceptacle)
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	--Lorath says filler line as player moves eye
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convEyeBuildup, idActorPlayer, actorLorath)
end
